{
  "message": "feat(helm): Add controller.enabled flag to skip controller deployment\n\nAdd controller.enabled parameter (default: true) to allow deploying\nonly VA/HPA/ServiceMonitor resources without a new controller instance.\n\nUse case: Monitor additional variants using an existing cluster-wide\nWVA controller without deploying duplicate controller instances.\n\nExample:\n  helm upgrade -i my-variant ./charts/workload-variant-autoscaler \\\n    --set controller.enabled=false \\\n    --set llmd.namespace=my-namespace \\\n    --set llmd.deploymentName=my-vllm-deployment\n\n\ud83e\udd16 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
